weka.core

类 Trie

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.core.Trie
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<String>, Collection<String>, RevisionHandler

    public class Trie
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable, Collection<String>, RevisionHandler
    A class representing a Trie data structure for strings. See also Trie on WikiPedia.
    版本:
    $Revision: 1.2 $
    作者:
    fracpete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz)
